{
  "stem": "2004.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And obviously, he was not as conditioned to the cold weather as some of us from Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were more conditioned to the cold weather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he froze.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He froze.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He died, so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But nobody really paid that much attention to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As you well know, it's every man for himself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I paid-- I knew he was dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was tight in space.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I do remember that one young man wanted to really sit on him to have a seat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then a lot of our people says, don't you dare, he says.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Find yourself another space.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do not sit on a dead body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it is-- it just goes against us, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he found himself another place because he wanted to make himself a little more comfortable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sitting-- instead of sitting on the floor, he was going to sit on a-- on a corpse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, you could imagine how hardened we were because in today, if I would see a corpse, I would be frightened.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Not that I didn't see enough in my day, but I did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at that time, it really didn't have-- you got so hardened, it really didn't have that much of an effect on you as it would have today because many years later, your outlook changes, and so on, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A hard decision?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Give me an example.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you mean by a hard decision?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Would I ever do-- did I ever do something that I didn't want to do?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never went out to my way to hurt anybody.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never-- let me put it to you this way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was looking out for number one, and I was number one.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
